# ==============================================================================
# Obsidian & Knowledge Base Overrides
# ==============================================================================

# Matrix_dev/ is Aditya's local Obsidian vault that drives the LLM
# knowledge engine. It is intentionally per-user and is NEVER pushed to
# the team repo. Notes, plans, schema-rationale docs live here; anything
# the team needs to act on gets surfaced as a separate file at the repo
# root (e.g. left_out_tasks.md) or as code.
Matrix_dev/

# Ignore Obsidian's visual UI state, workspace layouts, and local plugin caches
**/Matrix_dev/.obsidian/

# OPTIONAL: If you ever add an immutable 'sources/' folder for heavy web clips,
# raw PDFs, or long YouTube transcripts that you don't want bloating GitHub:
# **/Matrix_dev/sources/

# ==============================================================================
# Standard Python & Frontend Ignores
# ==============================================================================
backend/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/.next/
frontend/dist/
.DS_Store

# ==============================================================================
# Claude Code / agent runtime — local state, never push to repo
# Note: .claude/artifacts/ (refactor-plan, routes-manifest) is intentionally
# tracked from the initial commit. Only the per-user runtime paths below are
# ignored.
# ==============================================================================
.claude/agents/
.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/matrix-bd-*/
.claude/plans/
.claude/cache/
.claude/sessions/
.agents/
skills-lock.json
